18
00:02:15,630 --> 00:02:17,240
Should we forfeit?

19
00:02:17,240 --> 00:02:17,870
Forfeit?

20
00:02:17,870 --> 00:02:19,329
If Wen Chengye isn't here,

21
00:02:19,710 --> 00:02:20,910
