25
00:02:29,680 --> 00:02:31,030
Those who don't want to play

26
00:02:31,030 --> 00:02:32,520
can draw a cross on it.

27
00:02:33,560 --> 00:02:34,870
If there is even a single cross

28
00:02:34,870 --> 00:02:36,170
