in aerial duels.

149
00:10:29,000 --> 00:10:30,240
Then you can do it.

150
00:10:30,400 --> 00:10:32,250
No, how can Chen do it?

151
00:10:32,360 --> 00:10:32,960
If Chen drops back,

152
00:10:32,960 --> 00:10:34,150
