156
00:10:37,870 --> 00:10:39,630
I'm pretty good at clearing the ball.

157
00:10:39,630 --> 00:10:40,890
Bro, here's the thing.

158
00:10:41,200 --> 00:10:41,910
You're too soft on defense,

159
00:10:41,910 --> 00:10:43,080
